# First Person Trust Stack (FPS)

This is the **First Person Trust Stack** — a TypeScript monorepo for fpndtg.com product UX.

Before scaffolding, refactoring layout, or adding major features, read **`docs/SCAFFOLD-BRIEF.md`** in full.

Key facts:

- **Path A:** TypeScript product + HTTP adapters to live VTI at `*.fpndtg.com`
- **Not** part of verifiable-trust-infrastructure; never import VTI Rust crates here
- Entity model: VTA (keys) → VTC (community, issues VMC) → VTN (federation of VTCs, greenfield)
- Brand: `fpndtg.com`, Trust Tasks org `fpndtg` — no Affinidi/OpenVTC user-facing branding
- Phase 0 (VTI deploy smoke) was skipped intentionally

When user says "scaffold FPS" or similar, execute Phase 1 in SCAFFOLD-BRIEF.md.
